titles.title: To extend the temporary suspension of duty on phenyl (4,6-dimethoxy-pyrimidin-2-yl) carbamate.

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Ways and Means.

bill.summary: 10/22/2009--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to extend the temporary suspension of duty on phenyl (4,6-dimethoxy-pyrimidin-2-yl) carbamate.
